item.title: SPD 545: Shadow, Part I
item.description: This week on the podcast, we're just a pawn in Gerald Robotnik's schemes – because we're watching the Power Rangers SPD episode "Shadow, Part I"! Why is Doggie such a dick? How fast can you open a restaurant in Newtech City? And what in the name of Emperor Gruumm is a stevedore? The answers to these questions (and more!) await, on this episode of the Ranger Danger SPD podcast! Feed: http://rangerdangerpodcast.com/podcast-feed.xml

item.title: GPT 4.1: The New OpenAI Workhorse
item.description: We’ll keep this brief because we’re on a tight turnaround: GPT 4.1, previously known as the Quasar and Optimus models, is now live as the natural update for 4o/4o-mini (and the research preview of GPT 4.5)... Feed: https://rss.flightcast.com/vgnxzgiwwzwke85ym53fjnzu.xml
